# StreamPlotConsole - Real-Time Data Visualizer

StreamPlotConsole draws live line charts from incoming data streams for monitoring and visual feedback.

## Features
- Scrollable graph  
- Adjustable speed  
- Clean charting UI  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/22_StreamPlotConsole.git
cd 22_StreamPlotConsole
python visualize.py
